The past year, I’ve been faced with so many obstacles, so many ppl/things tried to break me but my faith, my God, and my determination to Grow Thru what I Go Thru wouldn’t allow me to break. Everything I’ve been through truly made me stronger. I turned every obstacle into a lesson and every lesson into a blessing.  This is the year of “Growth” for me!
And as I grow through my obstacles I want to encourage you all to do the same thing. Sometimes we can’t control what happens to us but we can control how we deal with it. Sometimes the one way to get through it, is it go through it and the best was to go through it is to grow through it. 
I encourage you all to Grow thru what you grow thru! 💞

Yepppppp…it’s ME!!!

Healing and growing will definitely add to your glow up. 
You find yourself being more confident and empowered. 
Things that you once tripped over become things you simply walk around. 

Realized that healing is a continuous process. You think you’re there and then “BAM” something or someone comes into your life and triggers you. You realize that although you have progressed…you still have work to be done. Sometimes I wonder if I’ll ever be completely healed but then I redirect my focus on not how far I have to go but on how far I’ve come. 

There’s a glow that comes with recognizing that you are investing in your emotional and mental well being. There’s joy in reclaiming your happiness. Don’t allow the steps that are ahead of you to make you forget the steps you’ve already taken. 

Be proud of your journey even if you haven’t quite reached your destination!!

I’m still a work in progress…but I’m definitely PROGRESSIVELY WORKING. And for that reason…I’m proud of ME!! 🤎💪🏾🤞🏾

#proudofme #thickgirls #mood #happyweight #thickthighssavelives #melanin #blackwomen #healthylifestyle #brownskingirls
Good Morning!!❣️🙏🏽

Stop blaming others for how they treat you and start asking YOURSELF why you accepted the unfavorable treatment. 

If they’re disrespecting you…ask YOURSELF why are you so comfortable with being disrespected. 

If they aren’t showing up for you…ask YOURSELF why are you still sending them invites. 

If they aren’t loving you properly…ask YOURSELF what part of you decided that you didn’t deserve to be genuinely loved.

And when you finish asking YOURSELF all those questions…do the work to heal THOSE parts of YOU. 

At the end of the day…you have a choice in what you accept for yourself. You have the power to deny access to anyone or anything that is not beneficial to the life you desire. Stop focusing on their actions and concentrate on your reactions. Stop trying to figure them out…and take some time to relearn YOU. 

Sometimes you got to heal yourself so that you can quickly identify the brokenness in others. 

Your healing has to be PERSONAL!!!💞

#healingYOU #prioritize #selflove #selfcare #findingpeace #inspirationalquotes #motivation #selfassessment #healingjourney #takecareofYOU #healedandwhole #accountability #growthmindset

Could’ve been a product of my environment, but I decided to become a product of my decisions! If you think about it, we’re all really one decision away from a better life. Decide what you want in life and go after it! The world is yours, and once you start to believe it, then and only then will you become whatever it is that you desire!

MAKE YOUR DREAMS, Reality!💎

Happy New Year!!🥂🖤🍾
